== Usage ==
Used to warn new editors that they have blanked a page or removed content without stating a reason and/or gaining consensus.
Using <nowiki>{{welcome-delete|Like this one}}</nowiki> references a specific article <nowiki>(You can put any article name after the | )</nowiki>

